Package: seader
Title: Access Public Data from Fundação SEADE
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Leonardo", "Fujisima", email = "leonardo@fujisimaanalytics.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools to access public datasets from Fundação SEADE,
    including vital statistics such as births. The package connects to
    externally stored datasets and returns Arrow datasets that can be
    queried lazily using dplyr. This package is not affiliated with,
    endorsed by, or maintained by Fundação SEADE.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
URL: https://github.com/fujisima/seader
BugReports: https://github.com/fujisima/seader/issues
Imports:
    arrow
Suggests:
    curl,
    dplyr,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
